
<!-- compliance:gdpr -->
## Compliance: GDPR

- WHEN collecting personal data, document lawful basis (Art. 6) in `docs/compliance/data-processing.md`.
- WHEN building a data-export or delete feature, ensure data-subject rights (Arts. 15-22) flow end-to-end.
- NEVER transfer personal data outside the EEA without SCCs or adequacy decision.
- Retention: every personal-data store must have a documented retention period + automatic deletion job.
- Breach notification: DPO informed within 72h; user-facing notification if high risk.
- Consent: granular, withdrawable, logged.
